{
  "stem": "2916.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Whether it was in the thousands, or only in the hundreds, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But once that number was admitted, then you had to wait for the next year's opening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And if the list was very long, it took years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So my father was told that the quota, is very-- the list is very long, and he has to wait his turn.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in 1938, before the Hungarians came, we already knew rumors that we'll be occupied by Hungary, and we'll be cut off from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father went to Prague and-- and submitted a special request that we are going to be cut off from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we are in danger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Perhaps, we could get some kind of a-- a-- preferential treatment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the American embassy told us, no, you have to wait your turn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later that year, in September, we were cut off from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from that point on, we were no longer on the Czechoslovak quota, because now we belong to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we could not put on names on the Hungarian quota from the American Embassy, because we were not considered Hungarian citizens.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were Jewish aliens from this point on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father was not a Hungarian citizen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some people who were born in Hungary could apply for Hungarian citizenship.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But then again, very soon the Jew law came out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all Jews, even in Hungary, lost their citizenship, which meant that we were not entitled to be registered on the American quota.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we were trapped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were really, really trapped and ready for Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we went to school until the German occupation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans came to Hungary unexpectedly on March 19, 1944.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "German troops marched into Budapest.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
